{
  "_comment": [
    "refresh-map.json — template → live-source map with the SHA-256 of each live source as of the last sync.",
    "Consumed by scripts/refresh-scope.sh (scan = incremental refresh scope; regen = re-baseline at release end).",
    "Template keys are relative to blueprint/. Source paths are relative to the source project root;",
    "{project:ROLE} tokens resolve via the project's .professor/manifest.json .interview.projects[ROLE]; leading ~/ resolves to $HOME (host-level sources).",
    "curated: true = hand-curated template with no live source — never auto-derived.",
    "Multi-source entries list every live file whose change forces re-derivation (representative-pattern templates).",
    "ignore_sources = live files deliberately not shipped (project-local); source_globs = the mined surfaces scanned for UNMAPPED-LIVE files."
  ],
  "source_globs": [
    "CLAUDE.md",
    ".claude/settings.json",
    ".claude/agents/*.md",
    ".claude/commands/**",
    ".claude/scripts/*.sh",
    ".claude/workflows/*.js",
    ".claude/output-styles/*.md",
    "{project:backend}/CLAUDE.md",
    "docs/agents/_index.md",
    "docs/agents/standards.md",
    "docs/commands/pcm/references/*",
    "docs/commands/git/references/*",
    "docs/commands/build/references/*",
    "docs/commands/animate/references/*",
    "docs/commands/documenter/references/**",
    "docs/commands/jc/references/*"
  ],
  "ignore_sources": [
    ".claude/commands/contentor.md",
    ".claude/commands/h/",
    "docs/commands/jc/references/deploy.md"
  ],
  "templates": {
